metadata.name: Bicycle day 2022
metadata.description:
Happy Bicycle Day!
The various dark things that have happened around the world recently have made me feel hopeless and lose faith in some of my core beliefs.
But today I want to celebrate faith, celebrate freedom.
Believe what you believe and believe that there’s truth in what you believe.
Don’t stop believing - keep your intentions strong. Where there is belief, there will be freedom.
We are all in this process together.
